test_even_range:
assert [87, 89, 91, 93] == []
  Left contains 4 more items, first extra item: 87
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [87, 89, 91, 93]
test_all_one_range:
assert [87, 89, 91, 93] == [1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, ...]
  At index 0 diff: 87 != 1
  Right contains 3 more items, first extra item: 1
  Full diff:
  - [1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1]
  + [87, 89, 91, 93]
